version_description: Full song version as seen here ( https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1P17ct4e5OE). Strumming patterns vary throughout the song and are based on Richie Blackmore's strumming in the video. Contains full song, chords and lyrics. Song begins in key of G then transposes to A after bridge. Although this is a chord tab, the guitar fills are notated.
